    <string name="cogTest_hitber_pick_test">Please tap on the diagnosis you want to perform</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_first_mission_instructions">Select the correct answer. To select the correct answer, click on the question.</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_shape_dialog_mission_instructions">You will see 5 shapes. Remember them for the next part of the mission. When you\'re ready, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_shape_mission_instructions">You will see several shapes. Select the 5 shapes you saw a few minutes ago by clicking on them. If you don\'t remember, you can guess. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_third_mission_instructions">For the next minute, numbers will appear in the center of the screen. Every time you see the number 7, tap on the screen. To start the task, click \"Start\". At the end of the task, a \"Thank you\" message will appear. Click \"Continue\" to proceed.</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_fourth_mission_instructions">Write what is shown in the image. To write your answer, click on the question. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_fifth_mission_instructions">In this part, you need to create a sentence from the words displayed in front of you. To place a word in the sentence, drag it to the slot of your choice. If you want to change the position of a word that is already placed, drag it from the word bank and place it again. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_repeat_sentence">Press the Listen button, listen to the sentence being spoken, then press the Speak button and repeat the sentence.</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_fridge_mission_instructions">In this part, you will be asked to complete a task. To listen to the task, click \"Listen\". When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_ball_drag_question1">Drag the black circle into the square. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_ball_drag_question2">Drag the yellow circle into the square. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_ball_drag_question3">Drag the blue circle into the square. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_ball_drag_question4">Drag the green circle into the square. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_ninth_mission_instructions">In this part, you need to create a sentence from the words displayed in front of you. To place a word in the sentence, drag it to the slot of your choice. If you want to change the position of a word that is already placed, drag it from the word bank and place it again. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>
    <string name="cogTest_hitber_tenth_mission_instructions">Copy the image displayed on the left to the center of the screen. Use the shapes on the right to copy the image. Drag and arrange the shapes in the center of the screen. When you\'re done, click \"Continue\".</string>

